Package org.primaresearch.ident

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Id
    Interface for IDs.

    Note: IDs should always be compared using the equals method as two different objects might represent the same ID.
    Identifiable
    Interface for objects having an ID.
    IdRegister
    Interface for central ID register that makes sure IDs are unique.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    XmlIdRegister
    IdRegister implementation for XML conform IDs.
    XmlIdRegister.XmlId
    Implementation of Id intended for XML id convention.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IdRegister.InvalidIdException
    Exception for duplicate or malformed IDs
